T1  - Finite-State Contract Theory with a Principal and a Field of Agents
AU  - Carmona, René
AU  - Wang, Peiqi
Y1  - 2020/12/28
PY  - 2020
DA  - 2021/08/01
N1  - doi: 10.1287/mnsc.2020.3760
