TY  - JOUR
T1  - Multiregional Oligopoly with Capacity Constraints
AU  - Alsabah, Humoud
AU  - Bernard, Benjamin
AU  - Capponi, Agostino
AU  - Iyengar, Garud
AU  - Sethuraman, Jay
Y1  - 2020/12/18
PY  - 2020
